\outl0\strokewidth0 \strokec2 Pipeline Monitoring\
\pard\pardeftab720\sl540\sa300\partightenfactor0

\f1\b0\fs32 \cf4 \strokec4 Airflow can surface metrics and emails to help you stay on top of pipeline issues.\
